This paper is about designing and evaluating a conversational system, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and human-computer interaction (HCI). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Additionally, the paper discusses the technical approach of crowd-sourcing content, which could fall under cs.SD (Software Engineering) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
